<para id="para-00004">In addition to databases, registries are available to provide guidance and information. <term id="term-00006">Registries</term> are collections of information regarding people and typically outline a specific condition or diagnosis (National Institutes of Health [NIH], 2023). [link]Table 11.5[/link] provides examples of commonly used registries and resources for nurses.</para>
